# List of State Register of Heritage Places in the Town of Port Hedland

The State Register of Heritage Places is maintained by the Heritage Council of Western Australia. , 81 places are heritage-listed in the Town of Port Hedland, of which seven are on the State Register of Heritage Places.
List
The Western Australian State Register of Heritage Places, , lists the following seven state registered places within the Town of Port Hedland:
